### Schema Requirements:
# All singleton endpoints support multilingual content using language keys (en, id)
# Common fields:
# - title: object with language keys
# - description: object with language keys
# - Images/media: valid URL strings
# - Colors: hex color codes
# - Contact info: email, phone number, address fields
# - All singleton data is upserted (create if not exists, update if exists)